Combine black-eye peas, bell pepper, celery, red onion, and onion in a large bowl; set aside. Combine SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, salt, pepper, garlic, vegetable oil, vinegar, and Sylvia's Hot Sauce(R); whisk until blended. Pour dressing over black-eye pea mixture, tossing gently to coat. Cover and chill overnight.